    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase the minimum holiday entitlement to 30 days including bank holidays",
        "additional_details": "It will help with public spending as everyone tends to spend more on there day off. It will also help with full time workers mental health, giving an extra 2 days off work when needed.",
        "background": "Make it mandatory for employers to give an extra 2 days off per year, making it 30 days holiday including bank holidays for full time workers.",
